    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presented in showroom-grade condition, this E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, producing 333hp through six individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual and a limited-slip differential. This example has been meticulously maintained with a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity. The suspension geometry remains precise, benefiting from refreshed bushings and original-spec dampers. A true driver's car with zero mechanical compromises and a flawless factory finish.",
