    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a true 'time capsule' specimen that defines the term 'mint.' This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a drop of rain. The exterior boasts its original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition, retaining that distinct new-car aroma. The premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the dashboard is free of any UV fading, and every single electronic feature\u2014from the infotainment system to the ambient lighting\u2014functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is spotless. This is not just a used car; it is a pristine example for the most discerning collector who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
