    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is an absolute dream\u2014it's in stunning, showroom-ready condition and looks like it just rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been pampered its whole life, and you won\u2019t find a single scratch or scuff anywhere. It drives like a total cloud and still has that fresh, new-car feel inside and out. Seriously, you\u2019ve gotta see it to believe it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this gem go to someone who will love it as much as I have! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 43250.0,
