    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This specimen has undergone a comprehensive mechanical refresh, including a proactive rod bearing replacement, VANOS solenoid overhaul, and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis retains its original damping characteristics with zero bushing deflection, while the exterior maintains its factory-applied finish with no signs of oxidation or rock chips. This is a turn-key collector piece with a flawless DME readout and a pristine undercarriage, representing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-division engineering.",
